headline: Barclays Lifts PT on Archer-Daniels-Midland Company (ADM) to $68 From $61
summary: Archer-Daniels-Midland Company (NYSE:ADM) is one of the best sugar stocks to buy according to hedge funds. Barclays lifted the price target on Archer-Daniels-Midland Company (NYSE:ADM) to $68 from $61 on February 19 and maintained an Equal Weight rating on the shares. In another development, BMO Capital adjusted the price target on the stock to $63 […]
